{"tid":1530311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"『人手置頂』903全港大三擺 終極目標封鎖18區","createTime":"2019-09-02T02:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T02:39:39.000Z","uid":152321,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef22231b278af77b841686f25981740ac9effe86","tid":1530311,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:25:59.000Z","msg":"902唔成功唔緊要 我地吸取到經驗 不完美 但會改善<br />\n903全港再發起大三擺 終極目標要封鎖18區 還香港人一個假日<br />\n903唔得仲有904 905 906 一日味封鎖到18區 一日都塞爆香港<br />\n<br />\n全部手足集中自己區 封死主要出入口<br />\n癱瘓黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n封死主要迴旋處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n倒灌車流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快閃隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n封印狗局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n切記切記 要封印所有犬隻出入口 保護大家安全<br />\n<br />\n香港人俾有錢佬同政府搾壓夠啦！<br />\n香港人應該擁有屬於自己嘅假期！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人 辛苦哂 係時候休息陣</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">封鎖18區<br />\n塞爆全香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"f6432c0f3a730fe69c54c904103d68e2e78b843b","tid":1530311,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>封鎖18區</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c49458f84a92546c4dc8926aa35c3599e1bd3e96","tid":1530311,"uid":152321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>塞爆全香港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c333a77dbbd67552e054eaca407de6d45ae5a